How to decimate number of faces with blender (i.e. size of the file)

- Info
  - File
    - Import -> stl

- Properties
  - Modifiers
    - Add Modifier -> Decimate
      - Collapse
        - Ratio -> 0.4
    - Add Modifier -> Decimate
      - Planar
        - Angle Limit -> 5degree
  - Change color if wanted

- Info
  - File
    - Export -> dae


